T02TD3358E:38b-1: tsanda ma h'a ro sha na s'a dha nam /
T02TD3358E:38b-3: gtum po chen po'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD3358E:38b-4: bcom ldan 'das gtum po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3358E:38b-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes su padma dkar po'i steng na nyi ma la h'um yig nag po de yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das gtum po chen po khros pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-6: zar ma'i me tog lta bu /
T02TD3358E:38b-7: ming gzhan gyis mi g-yo ba zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-8: mi g-yo ba mi mnyam pa'i spyan /
T02TD3358E:38b-10: mi bzad pa'i zhal chen po /
T02TD3358E:38b-11: rin po che'i dbu rgyan can mche bas ma mchu mnan pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-12: mgo bo'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD3358E:38b-13: spyan gnyis dkar zhing dmar ba /
T02TD3358E:38b-15: g-yon pa'i phyag gis zhags pa dang sdigs mdzub thugs kar bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3358E:38b-16: sprul dkar po mchod phyir thogs pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-17: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can rin po che sna tshogs kyis rnam par spras pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-18: zhabs g-yon pas la ma reg pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-19: zhabs g-yas pa cung zhig bteg pa /
T02TD3358E:38b-20: nyi ma'i 'od kyi phreng ba can gyi bdag nyid rnam par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3358E:38b-21: dam tshig sems dpa' dang ye shes sems dpa' bsgom pa sngon du 'gro bas mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan par bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3358E:38b-22: de nas bzlas pa ni aom tsanda ma h'a ro sha na h'um phat /
T02TD3358E:38b-23: gtum po chen po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3358E:38b-24: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3358E:38b-25: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur cing zhus pa'o//
